{"tid":2164852,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇：準備「千人計劃2.0」創造更職位","createTime":"2020-08-19T12:17:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T12:57:18.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"72eaab1ae15cf9ade17a882c39465d65c6775cbc","tid":2164852,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"財經事務及庫務局局長許正宇表示，早前推出的金融科技「千人計劃」，在一個多月內收到接近400份申請，當中超過110份已獲初步審批，可進行招聘程序，部分企業更已成功聘請新員工，局方已在準備「千人計劃2.0」﹐創造更多職位，並拓展至涵蓋金融業界的多個範疇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544711-20200819.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544711-20200819.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=0888f249\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1544711-20200819.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=3c41051c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1544711-20200819.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"24f7d1f09de5738e9db96903078d19e1d605eb32","tid":2164852,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:20:19.000Z","msg":"大鍊鋼，人多就有科技"},{"pid":"ff75ad199c2746ce5e50a1fdcbfa8f80ca2697f9","tid":2164852,"uid":75196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:21:05.000Z","msg":"係咪老千個千"},{"pid":"40b3a57f5dfed92b986962e3b4674385071c8752","tid":2164852,"uid":184581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"用法律去打壓手足同支持國安法<br />\n支持江樂士做下一批美國制裁人選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/aaronMCN/status/1295929570256998401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FaaronMCN%2Fstatus%2F1295929570256998401&d=MYvC0VRZm9a3oqKPvUvInKtywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=47768e1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/fr